{"tid":1182173,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"［地盤之花］建材回收 青年獲環保領袖獎","createTime":"2019-06-02T04:02:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-02T06:19:05.000Z","uid":13739,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"7b2efc26a12d8059547c247664983822ae8fd0e1","tid":1182173,"uid":13739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T04:02:50.000Z","msg":"建築工程消耗大量建築材料，其中不少塑膠物料，例如釘板工序中的過牆管、玻璃膠筒，以至泡沫塑料，均可回收利用。然而，本地有系統安排回收的公司甚少，工程期間產生的塑料大都被視為建築廢料，最終棄置於堆填區。<br />\n <br />\n鍥而不捨 環保先鋒<br />\n <br />\n文泳茵在一間工程公司擔任助理環保經理，公司在荃灣德士古道資助出售房屋發展計劃工地推動環保，其間她悉心部署，鼓勵工人重用建築物料，並積極安排回收塑膠物品。<br />\n<br />\n睇片啦<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.news.gov.hk/chi/2019/05/20190530/20190530_155355_325.html?type=ticker\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.news.gov.hk%2Fchi%2F2019%2F05%2F20190530%2F20190530_155355_325.html%3Ftype%3Dticker&d=nzMqhIG%2BVuPatXbgV3aJI4%2FGH25nCqGTJutLbOxS7Ms%3D&h=baba78c7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.news.gov.hk/chi/2019/05/20190530/20190530_155355_325.html?type=ticker</a>"},{"pid":"7ed0c980ecd783e5e135a7b2673c1b43ee923134","tid":1182173,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T04:24:14.000Z","msg":"游惠貞.jpg"},{"pid":"1ca4699f3bde9e11b623311f4ab6cb3f61e67518","tid":1182173,"uid":13739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T04:26:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30213281123ea305c0c6fa55f7293e4e3ab6a241","tid":1182173,"uid":13739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T04:27:03.000Z","msg":"有沒有ig"},{"pid":"2579793eae83877d488210da07406cb5d83007d1","tid":1182173,"uid":58512,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"